625
00:33:44.848 --> 00:33:46.372
Please...

626
00:33:46.546 --> 00:33:47.982
please just let me go.

627
00:33:48.156 --> 00:33:49.723
Please.

628
00:33:49.897 --> 00:33:52.595
Please. I'll do anything.

629
